What is Load Balancer 
    It allows the application traffic or requests distributes across multuple targets from a single point of contacts for the clients.


    
Types of LOAD BALANCERS

    Classic Load Balancer - 2025
    Application Load Balancer
    Network Load Balancer
    Gateway Load Balancer 




